categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: A Weequay male served as a member of the Ohnaka Gang, led by fellow Weequay pirate Hondo Ohnaka during the Clone Wars.

The Weequay participated in an operation to Felucia around 22 BBY, trying to extort a portion of a highly valuable crop of nysillin from a local farming community. When a scout sent to the village failed to report in, the Weequay reported his absence to Ohnaka.
This pirate was voiced by James Arnold Taylor, who also voices Obi-Wan Kenobi in The Clone Wars TV series.
